.FILL.JUST
The VERIFY can be performed on any Host regardless of the current file
.FILL.JUST
structure on the host.  No longer need to start it on one host, and then
finish it on the home host.  If a TAPE will not VERIFY, cycle in another
tape before doing the SAVE over from the tape that would not verify.
.LM 11
.NOFILL.NOJUST
