.TS 8,33
	<MESSAGE/^D^E^V^I^C^E	<MEANING
	--------------	-------
.SKIP 1
	<BINARY <DATA <INCOMPLETE	^LENGTH OF A BLOCK DISAGREES WITH THE
	   <PTR	WORD COUNT.
.SKIP 1
	<CKSUM <OR <PARITY <ERROR	^A READ OR WRITE ERROR HAS OCCURRED.
	   <ALL
.SKIP 1
	<INPUT <BUFFER <OVERFLOW	^A BLOCK IS TOO LARGE FOR THE BUFFERS.
	   <ALL
.SKIP 1
	<DEVICE <ERROR	^THE <DATA <CONTROL <UNIT FOR A DEVICE HAS
	   <ALL	DETECTED A LOSS OF DATA.
.SKIP 1
	<PHYSICAL <EOT	^THE END OF TAPE HAS BEEN REACHED.
	   <MTA,^F^T^A
